                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.6363/178a.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Vice
                        Consul <persName type="to">Bevan</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 30, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>If an engagement is threatened near Tampico, you will please confer immediately
                    with the respective leaders and caution them against the destruction of the oil
                    properties, pointing out the danger of conflagration and the possibility of
                    great damage being done to both life and property.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
